casebody.head_matter:
In re Larry COCHRAN, petitioner.
No. 16-6484.
Supreme Court of the United States
Nov. 28, 2016.
Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for writ of mandamus and/or prohibition is dismissed. See Rule 39.8.
Justice KAGAN took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
